{"tid":2067618,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不要問為什麼 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-06-17T06:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T06:23:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96d5b3cd67278a577dc790a87aee3eea71384128","tid":2067618,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20200617/20938554/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200617%2F20938554%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG4%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=7e2feaa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200617%2F20938554%2F&h=38f46e31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20200617/20938554/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n不要問為什麼 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200617/large/1592296118_9f0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200617%2Flarge%2F1592296118_9f0f.jpg&h=f2b7eee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共最近頻頻出手，誓要廢除香港自治，把一九八四年簽署的《中英聯合聲明》視如無物；英國無奈，朝野或主張收容香港的「英國海外國民」。五月二十九日，中共外交部發言人趙立堅警告說：「英國曾與我國交換備忘錄，明確承諾不會以居英權給予香港的『英國海外國民』，假如現在食言，就是違背國際法與國際關係基本準則，我國當有以應對。」他說來振振有詞。<br />\n<br />\n不過，論國際法與國際關係基本準則，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。明，卻要英國遵從外交備忘錄這些「已經完成其歷史任務」的「歷史文件」，究竟是什麼道理？<br />\n<br />\n而英國給港人居英權，是英國的事；港人選擇去英國而棄香港，則是個人自由，中共為什麼要反對？他們不是最不喜歡「干涉他國內政」的嗎？習近平的姊弟，不都是做了加拿大或澳洲公民嗎？當然，強權是不用講道理的。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n精挑細味 籽想好食，即like「籽想好食」FB專頁！"}]}